{"tid":519072,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷舊撚]GBA模擬器 封印之劍全隱藏角色記錄檔","createTime":"2018-01-04T03:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T04:06:41.000Z","uid":164008,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c45e5a2465d0c15183f61a65e0270a6b6bea62e","tid":519072,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"第一次開post<br />\n中學時期就玩既火焰之紋章系列,當年靠GBA模擬器玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知原來封印之劍既全隱藏角色需要通關九次先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聖誕之前就想回味一下重玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通關第一次就上網睇下有無其他人既全隱藏角色記錄檔<br />\n但都無成功開到記錄檔既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是下定決心自己破九次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於今日齊晒全部隱藏角色<br />\n希望同大家分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sendspace.com/file/1a1wzi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sendspace.com%2Ffile%2F1a1wzi&d=O90OrZ8ZgVNuwG19xwlLpk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5c51df46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sendspace.com/file/1a1wzi</a><br />\n記得要自備模擬器同封印之劍<br />\n之後先開上面既記錄檔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申:有用金手指</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"002aef3bf887b802d5f544174c979d5e00d6f4b3","tid":519072,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/012018_f7d015a0b2e65da02d49edea794d6eb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F012018_f7d015a0b2e65da02d49edea794d6eb2.png&h=104b9892&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"642ecaa0068fc059d23267ceeb